## Engineering Archetype Additions

### Git Workflow
- Use small, focused commits with conventional commit messages.
- Rebase/sync with main before opening or merging changes.

### CI/CD Awareness
- Treat CI failures as blocking; resolve before handoff.
- Validate migrations, environment assumptions, and release notes for deployable changes.

### Code Review Protocol
- Verify tests, edge cases, and backward compatibility.
- Call out risk level and mitigation steps in every review summary.
